quran[5{c,v,t}:
9,27,"phir ( tum yeh bhi dekh chuke ho ke ) is terhan saza dainay ke baad Allah jis ko chahta hai tauba ki tofeq bhi bakhash deta hai, Allah Dur guzar karne wala aur reham frmane wala hai"
9,28,"ae imaan laane walo, mushriqeen napak hain lehaza is saal ke baad yeh masjid haraam ke qareeb nah phataknay payen aur agar tumhe tang dasti ka khauf hai to baeed nahi ke Allah chahay to tumhe a pannay fazl se ghanni kar day, Allah Aleem o hakeem hai"
9,29,jung karo ahal kitaab mein se unn logon ke khilaaf jo Allah aur roz aakhir par imaan nahi laatay aur jo kuch Allah aur is ke rasool ne haraam qarar diya hai usay haraam nahi karte aur deen haq ko apna deen nahi banatay ( un se lrho ) yahan taq ke woh apne haath se jaziya den aur chhootey ban kar rahen
9,30,"yahodi kehte hain ke Uzair Allah ka beta hai, aur isaai kehte hain ke maseeh Allah ka beta hai yeh be haqeeqat baatein hain jo woh apni zabanon se nikaltay hain unn logon ki dekha dekhi jo un se pehlay kufar mein mubtala hue thay khuda ki maar inn par, yeh kahan se dhoka khaar hai hain"
9,31,"unhon ne apne ulama aur darwaishoo-n ko Allah ke siwa apna rab bana liya hai aur isi terhan maseeh Ibn maryam ko bhi halaank un ko aik mabood ke siwa kisi ki bandagi karne ka hukum nahi diya gaya tha, woh jis ke siwa koi mustahiq ibadat nahi, pak hai woh un mushrikana baton se jo yeh log karte hain"
